---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
import Header from '../components/Header.astro';
import Footer from '../components/Footer.astro';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="About | Food Additive Regulation Database"
  description="Learn about the Food Additive Regulation Database, a comprehensive resource for comparing food additive regulations across EU, USA, Japan, Australia/NZ, and Canada."
>
  <Header />

  <main class="bg-brand-50 pb-20">
    <!-- Hero Section -->
    <div class="bg-white border-b border-brand-100 mb-12">
      <div class="container py-16 text-center max-w-4xl mx-auto">
        <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-black text-brand-900 mb-6 leading-tight">
          About Food Additive <span class="text-accent">DB</span>
        </h1>
        <p class="text-xl text-brand-500 font-medium leading-relaxed max-w-2xl mx-auto italic">
          Empowering global consumers with factual, scientific data on food additives and international regulations.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="container max-w-4xl space-y-12">
      <section class="bg-white rounded-3xl p-8 md:p-12 shadow-sm border border-brand-100 prose prose-brand max-w-none">
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-brand-900 mb-6 flex items-center gap-3">
          <span class="w-1.5 h-6 bg-accent rounded-full"></span>
          What We Do
        </h2>
        <p class="text-brand-600 leading-relaxed text-lg">
          The Food Additive Regulation Database is a comprehensive resource for comparing food additive regulations across different countries and regions. We compile and present factual regulatory information about food additives from official government sources, making it easier to understand how different countries regulate the same substance.
        </p>

        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-8 mt-12 not-prose">
          <div class="bg-brand-50 p-6 rounded-2xl border border-brand-100">
            <h3 class="text-xs font-black uppercase tracking-widest text-brand-400 mb-4">Coverage</h3>
            <ul class="space-y-3 text-sm font-bold text-brand-900">
              <li class="flex items-center gap-2"><span>🇪🇺</span> European Union (EC 1333/2008)</li>
              <li class="flex items-center gap-2"><span>🇺🇸</span> United States (FDA 21 CFR)</li>
              <li class="flex items-center gap-2"><span>🇯🇵</span> Japan (MHLW Lists)</li>
              <li class="flex items-center gap-2"><span>🇦🇺</span> Australia & NZ (FSANZ)</li>
              <li class="flex items-center gap-2"><span>🇨🇦</span> Canada (Health Canada)</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
          <div class="bg-brand-50 p-6 rounded-2xl border border-brand-100">
            <h3 class="text-xs font-black uppercase tracking-widest text-brand-400 mb-4">Primary Sources</h3>
            <ul class="space-y-3 text-sm font-bold text-brand-900">
              <li class="flex items-center gap-2"><span class="w-1.5 h-1.5 bg-accent rounded-full"></span> EFSA (EU)</li>
              <li class="flex items-center gap-2"><span class="w-1.5 h-1.5 bg-accent rounded-full"></span> FDA (USA)</li>
              <li class="flex items-center gap-2"><span class="w-1.5 h-1.5 bg-accent rounded-full"></span> JECFA (WHO/FAO)</li>
              <li class="flex items-center gap-2"><span class="w-1.5 h-1.5 bg-accent rounded-full"></span> MHLW (Japan)</li>
              <li class="flex items-center gap-2"><span class="w-1.5 h-1.5 bg-accent rounded-full"></span> Health Canada</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>

      <div class="bg-brand-900 rounded-3xl p-8 md:p-12 text-white shadow-xl relative overflow-hidden">
        <div class="absolute top-0 right-0 -mr-16 -mt-16 w-64 h-64 bg-accent/20 rounded-full blur-3xl pointer-events-none"></div>
        
        <h2 class="text-xl font-bold mb-8 flex items-center gap-3 relative z-10">
          <span class="w-1.5 h-6 bg-accent rounded-full"></span>
          Operator & Contact
        </h2>
        
        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-12 relative z-10">
          <div class="space-y-4">
            <p class="text-brand-300 text-sm leading-relaxed font-medium">
              This database is part of the <strong class="text-white">Matrix DB</strong> project, which creates specialized cross-reference databases for various domains.
            </p>
            <div class="pt-4 border-t border-white/10">
              <div class="text-[10px] font-black uppercase tracking-widest text-brand-500 mb-2">Operator</div>
              <p class="text-brand-100 font-bold">SHOYA KIHARA</p>
            </div>
            <div>
              <div class="text-[10px] font-black uppercase tracking-widest text-brand-500 mb-2">Location</div>
              <p class="text-brand-100 font-bold text-sm">Fukuoka, Japan</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          
          <div class="bg-white/5 border border-white/10 p-6 rounded-2xl">
            <div class="text-[10px] font-black uppercase tracking-widest text-accent mb-4">Direct Contact</div>
            <p class="text-xl font-bold mb-4">contact@matrix-db.com</p>
            <p class="text-xs text-brand-400 italic">For questions, corrections, or feedback, please reach out via email.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <section class="bg-white rounded-3xl p-8 md:p-12 shadow-sm border border-brand-100">
        <h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-brand-900 mb-6 flex items-center gap-3">
          <span class="w-1.5 h-6 bg-accent rounded-full"></span>
          Critical Disclaimer
        </h2>
        <div class="p-6 bg-restricted-bg border border-restricted-border rounded-2xl">
          <p class="text-brand-900 font-bold leading-relaxed">
            This database provides factual regulatory information only. We do NOT provide medical, nutritional, or safety advice.
          </p>
          <p class="text-brand-600 text-sm mt-4 leading-relaxed italic font-medium">
            Regulatory status varies by country and may change without notice. Always refer to your local regulatory authority for the most current information and consult with qualified professionals for specific applications.
          </p>
        </div>
      </section>
    </div>
  </main>

  <Footer />
</BaseLayout>
